trans-unit.source: By enabling this extension you consent to sharing your data with an external system. Your use of this extension may be subject to additional licensing terms from AMC. To enable the service you must read and accept the terms of use.

trans-unit.source: The AMC Banking 365 Fundamentals extension saves you time and reduces errors when you send data to your bank. The extension uses the AMC Banking 365 Business service to transform data from Microsoft Dynamics 365 Business Central into formats that banks require. You specify the bank, and the extension does the rest. For more information, see the documentation.
trans-unit.target: L'estensione AMC Banking 365 Fundamentals consente di risparmiare tempo e ridurre gli errori quando si inviano i dati alla banca. L'estensione utilizza il servizio AMC Banking 365 Business per trasformare i dati di Microsoft Dynamics 365 Business Central nei formati richiesti dalle banche. È sufficiente specificare la banca e l'estensione fa il resto. Per ulteriori informazioni, vedere la documentazione.
